      "content": "It is completely understandable that the word \"healing\" feels inadequate when you feel so fundamentally changed. Right now, instead of focusing on 'fixing' the past self, perhaps shifting the focus to understanding the present self could be a gentle step. You are not merely \"haunting\" your life; you are enduring a significant internal shift, and that massive change deserves immense compassion. Speaking with a professional can help validate this profound sense of loss without the pressure of having to instantly \"fix\" something.",
      "source": "target",
