    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's hard to have compassion for something that feels so empty. like, why am i even trying to \"understand\" this version of me? it's just a burden. it feels like i'm just a mistake that keeps happening every single day, taking up room that someone else could actually use. there's no purpose to a shadow.",
