      "content": "Please hear this: your presence and your experience have inherent value, regardless of how empty it feels from the inside. When you feel like a burden, it is a symptom of deep pain, not an objective truth about who you are. Even in this shadowed space, there is a part of you that is hurting enough to seek understanding, and *that* part deserves care. Even small acts of kindness toward yourself right now are not wastes of space; they are acts of fundamental self-preservation.",
      "source": "target",
